&lt;li&gt;Deliver internal infrastructure services such as monitoring, logging, and alerting to internal users.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expand and enhance our Kubernetes-based application environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
